719382f-b.title: Manhattan: Dyckman Street - Nagle Avenue
719382f-b.text:
(1)
Dyckman Street, east from but not including Nagle Ave., showing
a portion of Highbridge Park,bordering on the south side of the street.
In the background appears the western shore of the Borough of the Bronx.
April 20, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
The same, at a point slightly eastward, from a different angle.
April 20, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(3)
A detail of Highbridge Park, seen in the two prior views.
April 20, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
